[section Sources]

a =/src/CMakeLists.txt= file, if provided, must always start with the following:

[pre
include(NT2Module)
nt2_module_source_setup([~module])
]

This =CMakeLists.txt= may then proceed to build libraries with `nt2_module_add_library`, or trigger the automatic generation of certain files with
`nt2_module_configure_file`, `nt2_module_postconfigure` or `nt2_module_configure_toolbox`.

[endsect]
